d)	The Municipal Treasurer in coordination with the Municipal Accountant and the Inventory Committee, examine the existence of the reported inventory account balances, prepare and submit the corresponding SSMI, together with the duly accomplished RIS, as basis for the recording of the necessary expenses/adjustments.

We recommended the following:

a)	The Municipal Accountant and Municipal Treasurer reconcile their accounting and property records, respectively, with the RPCPPE prepared by the Inventory Committee;


